wdi2-NY.GNS.ICTR.CN.def: Gross savings are calculated as gross national income less total consumption, plus net transfers. Data are in current local currency.
wdi2-NY.GNS.ICTR.CN.name: Gross savings
wdi2-NY.GNS.ICTR.CN.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
